    "answer_id" : 51722611,
    "question_id" : 26699385,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In addition to <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/41462567/2065796\">Ahmet's answer</a> you can add line breaks to the coma separated string using <code>&gt;</code> symbol.</p>\n\n<p><strong>application.yml</strong>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>ignoreFilenames: &gt;\n  .DS_Store, \n  .hg\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Java code</strong>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>@Value(\"${ignoreFilenames}\")    \nString[] ignoreFilenames;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
