      "comment_id" : 100031833,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "That works. In my case though the application failed, unless I add <code>@Configuration</code> at the beginning of the class in <code>ConfigProvider.java</code>. Otherwise i got <b>Source required a bean of type &#39;java.util.List&#39; that could not be found.</b>"
