      "body" : "I prefer the first version with &gt; though. If you put comment (e.g. after every line) IDE (IntelliJ) won&#39;t highlight the comment it in the first case but highlights it in the second case. It seems like it is supported to put the comment in the second case but it is not. The parser fails in both cases if the comment is there (spring-boot 2.2.10)."
