    "question_id" : 26699385,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Well, the only thing I can make it work is like so: </p>\n\n<pre><code>servers: &gt;\n    dev.example.com,\n    another.example.com\n\n@Value(\"${servers}\")\nprivate String[] array;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And dont forget the @Configuration above your class....</p>\n\n<p>Without the \",\" separation, no such luck...</p>\n\n<p>Works too (boot 1.5.8 versie)</p>\n\n<pre><code>servers: \n       dev.example.com,\n       another.example.com\n</code></pre>\n"
