    "body" : "<p>Configuration in yaml file:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-yaml prettyprint-override\"><code>ignore:\n    filenames: &gt;\n        .DS_Store\n        .hg\n</code></pre>\n<p>In spring component:</p>\n<pre><code>@Value(&quot;#{'${gnore.filenames}'.split(' ')}&quot;)\nprivate List&lt;String&gt; igonoredFileNames;\n</code></pre>\n<p>This worked fine for me.</p>\n"
